msgid ""
"**YunoHost** is a system that installs itself on a **server**  \n"
"and allows you to install and maintain - **with very little technical "
"knowledge** -  \n"
"digital services (apps) **that you control**."
msgstr ""
"**Zerbitzari** batean instalatzen den sistema da **YunoHost**  \n"
"eta **zure kontrolpean** dauden zerbitzu digitalak (aplikazioak) instalatzea "
"eta mantentzea ahalbidetzen du  \n"
"**ezagutza tekniko oso urriarekin**."

