msgid "Donate to YunoHost!"
msgstr "Eman dohaintza YunoHost-i!"

msgid ""
"YunoHost has been around **since 2012** and is essentially developed **on a "
"voluntary basis** and **outside the commercial sector**."
msgstr ""
"YunoHost **2012az geroztik** da, eta, funtsean, **boluntarioek garatzen "
"dute** **merkataritza-sektoretik** kanpo."

msgid ""
"YunoHost is a modest project in terms of the resources it mobilizes - yet an "
"ambitious one, as much for its activism as for its technical and interface "
"design, as well as for the required perseverance to package and maintain the "
"hundreds of applications in our catalog."
msgstr ""
"YunoHost proiektua apala da darabiltzan baliabideei dagokienez, baina "
"anbizio handikoa: bai bere aktibismoagatik, bai diseinu teknikoagatik eta "
"interfazeagatik, baita gure katalogoko ehunka aplikazioak paketatzeko eta "
"mantentzeko behar den iraunkortasunagatik ere."

msgid ""
"If, like us, you'd like to see the project **continue to function**, evolve "
"to **meet its promises**, and allow us to **take care of the community**, "
"this is where you can donate!"
msgstr ""
"Guk bezala, proiektuaren **iraunkortasuna bermatu** eta **agindutakoa "
"betetzeko** eboluzionatu dezala nahi baduzu, eta **komunitatea zaintzeko** "
"aukera eman nahi badiguzu, hemen eman dezakezu dohaintza!"

