msgid "General questions about donations"
msgstr "Dohaintzei buruzko galdera orokorrak"

msgid "Will my donation be tax deductible?"
msgstr "Zerga-kengarria izango al du nire dohaintzak?"

msgid ""
"At this time, we do not provide tax-deductible donation receipts. We can, "
"however, issue donation receipts for your accounting purposes."
msgstr ""
"Une honetan ez dugu ematen dohaintzaren ordainagiririk kengarri "
"fiskalerako . Hala ere, dohaintza-ordainagiriak jaulki ditzakegu zure "
"kontabilitate-helburuetarako."

msgid ""
"My donation is not sent to YunoHost but to the Support Self-Hosting "
"association. Is this normal?"
msgstr ""
"Nire dohaintza ez da YunoHost-era bidaltzen, Support Self-Hosting elkartera "
"baizik. Normala al da hori?"

msgid ""
"Yes, that's expected, Support Self-Hosting is the association that enables "
"the YunoHost project to collect donations and pay expenses."
msgstr ""
"Bai, Support Self-Hosting da YunoHost proiektua dohaintzak kobratzeko eta "
"gastuak ordaintzeko gaitzen duen elkartea."

msgid "Can I become a member of the Support Self-Hosting association?"
msgstr "Support Self-Hosting elkarteko kide izan naiteke?"

msgid ""
"No: this is an association whose members are chosen by co-option.<br>We "
"don't think you need to be a member of Support Self-Hosting to contribute to "
"the YunoHost project. Anyone can come and help on most of our projects, and "
"we do our best to welcome volunteers."
msgstr ""
"Ez: elkarteko kideak kooperatiba bidez aukeratzen dira. Ez dugu uste Support "
"Self-Hosting elkarteko kide izan behar duzunik YunoHost proiektuan parte "
"hartzeko.<br> Edonor etor daiteke gure proiektu gehienetan laguntzera, eta "
"ahal dugun guztia egiten dugu boluntarioak hartzeko."

msgid ""
"I can't make a recurring donation, but I'd like to support YunoHost. What "
"can I do?"
msgstr ""
"Ezin dut dohaintza errepikakor bat egin, baina YunoHost babestu nahiko nuke. "
"Zer egin dezaket?"

msgid ""
"Thank you for your support and commitment.<br>You can make a one-off "
"donation directly from the [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost."
"org) page."
msgstr ""
"Eskerrik asko zure laguntza eta konpromisoagatik.<br>Dohaintza puntual bat "
"egin dezakezu zuzenean [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) "
"orritik."

msgid ""
"I've made a monthly donation but I've made a mistake in the amount or I'd "
"like to change it. How do I proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Hilero egiteko dohaintza bat programatu dut, baina zenbatekoan hanka sartu "
"dut edo aldatu nahiko nuke. Nola egin dezaket?"

msgid ""
"We cannot change the amount for future debits.<br>But you can cancel your "
"previous donation and start a new one by using the “Manage your monthly "
"donation” link on our [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Ezin dugu aldatu etorkizuneko zordunketen zenbatekoa.<br>Baina aurreko "
"dohaintza bertan behera utz dezakezu, eta beste bat hasi, gure [donate."
"yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) orrialdeko “Kudeatu zure hileko "
"dohaintza” estekaren bidez."

msgid ""
"I am currently making a recurring donation but my credit card has expired. "
"What should I do?"
msgstr ""
"Une honetan dohaintza errepikakor bat egiten ari naiz, baina nire kreditu-"
"txartela iraungi egin da. Zer egin behar dut?"

msgid ""
"Typically, your recurring donation is automatically interrupted once your "
"card has been deactivated.<br>To update your bank details with Support Self-"
"Hosting, please complete the form on the [donate.yunohost.org](https://"
"donate.yunohost.org) page as if it were your first donation."
msgstr ""
"Normalean, zure dohaintza errepikarkorra automatikoki eteten da zure "
"txartela desaktibatu ondoren.<br>Zure banku-datuak Support Self-Hosting-ekin "
"eguneratzeko, bete ezazu [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) "
"orriko formularioa, zure lehen dohaintza balitz bezala."

msgid ""
"My organization doesn't have a credit card, but would like to make a "
"donation. How do I go about it?"
msgstr ""
"Nire erakundeak ez du kreditu-txartelik, baina dohaintza bat egin nahi nuke. "
"Nola egin dezaket?"

msgid ""
"You can contact us so that we can provide you with an IBAN to make a bank "
"transfer."
msgstr ""
"Gurekin jar zaitezke harremanetan IBAN zenbakia eman diezazugun banku-"
"transferentzia bat egiteko."

msgid "I'd like to stop a recurring donation. What can I do?"
msgstr "Dohaintza errepikakor bat geldiarazi nahi nuke. Zer egin dezaket?"

msgid ""
"You can cancel your donation by using the “Manage your monthly donation” "
"link on our [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate.yunohost.org) page."
msgstr ""
"Zure dohaintza ezeztatu dezakezu gure [donate.yunohost.org](https://donate."
"yunohost.org) orrialdeko “Kudeatu zure hileko dohaintza” estekaren bidez."

msgid ""
"With **YunoHost**, easily manage %(a server|a cloud|a website|mailboxes|a "
"wiki|a social network|a video library|a blog|surveys|an accounting board|a "
"game server|a forum|a chat|an ERP)%  \n"
"for your friends, your association, your company"
msgstr ""
"Kudeatu modu errazean zure %(zerbitzaria|hodeia|webgunea|posta elektronikoa|"
"wikia|gizarte-sarea|bideo-liburutegia|bloga|inkestak|kontabilitate-arbela|"
"joko-zerbitzaria|foroa|bat-bateko mezularitza|ERPa)% YunoHostekin  \n"
"zure lagunentzat, elkartearentzat, enpresarentzat"

msgid "Carousel"
msgstr "Karrusela"

msgid "Slide controls"
msgstr "Diapositiben nabigazioa"

msgid "User portal: dark mode"
msgstr "Erabiltzaile-ataria: itxura iluna"

msgid "User portal: light mode with app description"
msgstr "Erabiltzaile-ataria: itxura argia eta aplikazioen deskribapena"

msgid "Administration panel: homepage"
msgstr "Administrazio-ataria: hasierako orria"

msgid "Administration panel: app catalog"
msgstr "Administrazio-ataria: aplikazioen katalogoa"

msgid "Administration panel: app installation"
msgstr "Administrazio-ataria: aplikazioen instalazioa"

msgid ""
"Screenshot of the user portal from which users can access the apps installed "
"on the server, listing several applications installed."
msgstr ""
"Erabiltzaile-atariaren pantaila-argazkia. Erabiltzaileak zerbitzarian "
"instalatutako aplikazioetara sartzea ahalbidetzen dioen eremua da. Aplikazio "
"ugari ageri dira instalatuta."

msgid ""
"Screenshot of the user portal from which users can access the apps installed "
"on the server, light version with description of each app."
msgstr ""
"Erabiltzaile-atariaren pantaila-argazkia. Erabiltzaileak zerbitzarian "
"instalatutako aplikazioetara sartzea ahalbidetzen dioen eremua da. Kolore "
"argiak erakusten ditu. Aplikazio bakoitzaren deskribapena ageri da."

msgid ""
"Screenshot of the web administration panel displaying the following "
"categories: users, domains, apps, upgrade, services, tools and backup"
msgstr ""
"Administrazio-atariaren pantaila-argazkia. Honako eremuak ikusten dira: "
"erabiltzaileak, domeinuak, aplikazioak, sistemaren eguneraketak, zerbitzuak, "
"tresnak eta babeskopiak"

msgid ""
"Screenshot of the web administration panel displaying the app catalog for "
"the \"publication\" category, listing some apps available in the catalog."
msgstr ""
"Administrazio-atariaren pantaila-argazkia. Aplikazioen katalogoko "
"\"argitalpenak\" kategoria erakusten du, katalogoan eskuragai dauden zenbait "
"aplikazio zerrendatuz."

msgid ""
"Screenshot of the web administration panel displaying the app install form "
"when installing the Nextcloud application. The interface asks a few "
"technical questions regarding settings for the installation."
msgstr ""
"Administrazio-atariaren pantaila-argazkia. Nextcloud aplikazioaren "
"instalazio-pantaila ageri da. Interfazeak instalazioarekin zerikusia duten "
"galdera tekniko batzuk erakusten ditu."

msgid "Previous slide"
msgstr "Aurreko diapositiba"

msgid "Next slide"
msgstr "Hurrengo diapositiba"

msgid "Huh, but why <i class='fa fa-question fa-xs fa-width-auto'></i>"
msgstr "E, baina zergatik <i class='fa fa-question fa-xs fa-width-auto'></i>"

msgid "Try"
msgstr "Probatu"

msgid "Examples of uses"
msgstr "Erabilera adibideak"

msgid "For you and your friends"
msgstr "Zuretzat eta lagunentzat"

msgid "synchronize your calendars and contacts"
msgstr "sinkronizatu egutegiak eta kontaktuak"

msgid "keep your passwords and notes safe"
msgstr "mantendu pasahitzak eta oharrak toki seguruan"

msgid "host mailboxes"
msgstr "ostatatu posta elektronikoa"

msgid "organize your photos, videos and music"
msgstr "antolatu argazkiak, bideoak eta musika"

msgid "join alternative social media"
msgstr "bat egin gizarte-sare alternatiboekin"

msgid "For small organizations"
msgstr "Erakunde txikientzat"

msgid "host your own website"
msgstr "ostatatu zure webgunea"

msgid "share files in common (e.g. with Nextcloud)"
msgstr "partekatu fitxategiak (Nextcloudekin esaterako)"

msgid "edit multiple documents in real time"
msgstr "editatu dokumentu bat baino gehiago aldi berean"

msgid "manage your accounting"
msgstr "kudeatu kontabilitatea"

msgid "set up a team chat"
msgstr "antolatu taldeko txata"

msgid "Explore the app catalog"
msgstr "Arakatu aplikazioen katalogoa"

msgid "How to get started"
msgstr "Nola hasi"

msgid ""
"If you're not sure yet on, we invite you to [try the demo](https://doc."
"yunohost.org/try),  \n"
"and take a look at [the pros and cons](https://doc.yunohost.org/selfhosting) "
"of managing a server yourself.\n"
"\n"
"Take the time to think about what applications, what type of hardware and "
"what domain name you want for your server."
msgstr ""
"Oraindik ziur ez bazaude, [demoa](https://doc.yunohost.org/try) probatzera "
"gonbidatzen zaitugu,   \n"
"eta zerbitzari propioa kudeatzearen [abantailak eta desabantailak] "
"aztertzera.\n"
"\n"
"Hartu denbora zerbitzarirako zein aplikazio, zein hardware mota eta zein "
"domeinu nahi duzun pentsatzeko."

msgid "Choosing a support"
msgstr "Aukeratu euskarria"

msgid "ARM board / Raspberry Pi"
msgstr "ARM txartela / Raspberry Pi"

msgid "Old tower or portable (*ordinosaur*)"
msgstr "Dorre edo eramangarri zaharra (\"ordenasauroa\")"

msgid "Online server (VPS)"
msgstr "VPS zerbitzaria"

msgid "Compare"
msgstr "Alderatu"

msgid "Install YunoHost"
msgstr "Instalatu YunoHost"

msgid "Check the prerequisites<br>then flash or install the system"
msgstr "Egiaztatu betekizunak<br>eta instalatu sistema"

msgid ""
"YunoHost will guide you through setting up the first admin, the domain name "
"and your Internet router."
msgstr ""
"YunoHostek lehen administratzailea, domeinua eta Interneteko routerra "
"konfiguratzen lagunduko dizu."

msgid "Installation guide"
msgstr "Instalazio-gida"

msgid "Enjoy!"
msgstr "Gozatu!"

msgid "Install applications<br>in just a few clicks"
msgstr "Instalatu aplikazioak<br>klik apur batzuetan"

msgid "Set up backups"
msgstr "Konfiguratu babeskopiak"

msgid "Take care of your server"
msgstr "Zaindu zure zerbitzaria"

msgid "Guided tour"
msgstr "Ibilbide gidatua"

msgid "Previous articles"
msgstr "Artikulu zaharragoak"

msgid ""
"**YunoHost** is a non-profit **technocritical** project, developed and "
"maintained by **volunteers**."
msgstr ""
"**YunoHost** irabazi-asmorik gabeko proiektu **teknokritikoa** da, "
"**boluntarioek** garatzen eta mantentzen dutena."

msgid ""
"We advocate a **decentralized** Internet, with **open**, **interoperable** "
"technologies that **respect privacy** and **empowers people**."
msgstr ""
"Internet **deszentralizatu**aren alde egiten dugu, **pribatutasuna "
"errespetatzen** duten eta **pertsonak ahalduntzen** dituzten teknologia "
"**ireki** eta **elkarreragingarri**ekin."

msgid ""
"In addition, we aim to **give materiality back to the digital**, and "
"encourage **sobriety** and **reuse**."
msgstr ""
"Gainera, gure xedea **digitalak materialtasuna berreskuratzea** da, eta "
"**soiltasuna** eta **berrerabilpena** sustatzea."

msgid "Code repositories"
msgstr "Kode gordailuak"

msgid "They support us <3"
msgstr "Babesa ematen digute <3"

msgid ""
"We are thankful for our sponsors providing us with infrastructure and grants!"
msgstr ""
"Eskertuta gaude gure babesleek azpiegitura eta dirulaguntzak emateagatik!"

